pageContext.claim: “Pelosi doesn't want to hand over The Articles of Impeachment, which were fraudulently produced by corrupt politicians like Shifty Schiff in the first place, because after all of these years of investigations and persecution, they show no crimes and are a joke and a scam!”
pageContext.analysis: The articles of impeachment were delivered to the Senate on Jan. 15, 2020. Presidential impeachments are not required to based on "crimes."
